  "description": {
    "en": "Herbal preparation derived from Kushen. Kushen is a cold, bitter herb made from the roots of the sophora plant that enters the heart, liver, stomach, large intestine and bladder meridians. It is used to clear heat, dispel wind and dampness,..."
